                                                <div class="content_text" style="text-align:left;padding: 0;">
                                                    The formative evaluation of the students is done as per University
                                                    rules. The evaluation process is transparent and robust. There is a
                                                    two-tier system of evaluation. External evaluation is conducted by
                                                    the
                                                    University at the end of each semester.
                                                    <br/>
                                                    <br/>
                                                    The dates of external evaluation
                                                    are announced very early through the university website and other
                                                    media.
                                                    The internal examinations are conducted as part of internal
                                                    evaluation.
                                                    Attendance, Performance in assignments and seminars also taken into
                                                    account in awarding internal marks. Academic Monitoring Cell control
                                                    the
                                                    internal evaluation process. Grievance redressal mechanism operates
                                                    both
                                                    at the department and institutional level
                                                </div>
